# Vercel deploy = browser-runtime files ONLY.
#
# Everything is excluded by default; only the allowlisted files below are
# deployed. This keeps tenant PII (data/*.json, knowledge-base/ outputs with
# rents & contacts, etc.) OUT of the public Vercel bundle — in production the
# dashboard reads that data from Firestore (auth-gated), never from static files.
#
# Allowlist syntax: ignore all top-level entries, then re-include specifics.

/*

!index.html
!firebase-config.js
!crosby-data.js
!vercel.json
